 <entry>
   <title>Light-box</title>
   <link href="/portfolio/light-box.html"/>
   <updated>2015-03-20T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
   <id>/portfolio/light-box</id>
   <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;This coursework requires you to design an interface for consumers to confgure an hypothetical IoT device that has no keyboard nor high resolution visual display. The “Light-box” is designed to increase remote awareness of two households. It needs to be connected to an existing Wi-Fi network to connect to the internet, and in turn, to another light- box.&lt;/p&gt;

